OL,4,CNottingham attacks put into special
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police has been put
OL,8,Finto special measures following
OL,9,Fconcerns about how it carries out
OL,10,Finvestigations and deals with victims.
OL,12,FThe force has been told to "urgently
OL,13,Fproduce an improvement plan" by a
OL,14,Fwatchdog.
