OL,4,CNottingham attacks put into special
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FHis Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,8,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,9,FServices (HMICFRS) announced the move
OL,10,Fon Monday which sees the East Midlands
OL,11,Fforce subjected to what the body `
OL,12,Fwhich scrutinises the performance of
OL,13,Fforces in England and Wales ` calls an
OL,14,F"enhanced level of monitoring" under
OL,15,Fwhat is known as the "engage" process.
OL,17,FNottinghamshire joins five other
OL,18,Fforces currently in special measures,
OL,19,Fincluding the Metropolitan Police,
OL,20,FWest Midlands, Staffordshire, Devon
OL,21,Fand Cornwall, and Wiltshire.
