OL,7,FThe reasons behind the decision have
OL,8,Fnot yet been laid out, but will be
OL,9,Fdetailed in an inspection report due
OL,10,Fto be published later this year.
OL,12,FThe move has been welcomed by the
OL,13,Ffamilies of Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,14,FO'Malley-Kumar, who died were stabbed
OL,15,Fto death by Valdo Calocane in
OL,16,FNottingham last year.
OL,18,FThe HMICFRS has confirmed that the
OL,19,Fdecision is not related to the force's
OL,20,Fhandling of the Valdo Calocane case.
