OL,7,FIn a statement, the Webber and
OL,8,FO'Malley-Kumar families said: "Our
OL,9,Fcriticisms are aimed at the leadership
OL,10,Fof both forces and also the management
OL,11,Fand failures of the senior
OL,12,Finvestigating officer in the
OL,13,FNottinghamshire force in charge of our
OL,14,Fown case.
OL,16,F"We welcome the news today that the
OL,17,FHMICFRS recognise that Nottinghamshire
OL,18,FPolice require intervention and urgent
OL,19,Fimprovement and that they have
OL,20,Feffectively been placed into 'special
OL,21,Fmeasures'.
OL,26,@pD@_OUxD@AOU
