OL,7,F"As families we have been very clear
OL,8,Fin the concerns we have raised
OL,9,Fregarding Nottinghamshire Police.
OL,11,F"Not only in the investigation itself
OL,12,Finto the murder of our loved ones, but
OL,13,Falso in the failures, missed
OL,14,Fopportunities, lessons and poor
OL,15,Fcommunication before, during and after.
OL,17,F"The IOPC are carrying out
OL,18,Finvestigations into Nottinghamshire
OL,19,Fand Leicestershire constabularies and
OL,20,Fwe have our first meeting with them on
OL,21,Fthe March 26.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@AOU
