OL,7,F"During this meeting we intend to
OL,8,Fprovide thorough detail and evidence
OL,9,Fto back up all of our concerns."
OL,11,FAn HMICFRS spokeswoman said: "This
OL,12,Fdecision is not related to the force's
OL,13,Fhandling of the Valdo Calocane case,"
OL,14,Fadding: "We did not look at the
OL,15,Fspecific circumstances of this case."
