OL,7,FThe under-fire force is already facing
OL,8,Fprobes from regulator the Independent
OL,9,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) and
OL,10,Fthe College of Policing amid
OL,11,Faccusations of a series of failings in
OL,12,Fthe wake of Calocane's killings.
OL,14,FValdo Calocane was sentenced to an
OL,15,Findefinite hospital order last month
OL,16,Ffor stabbing to death university
OL,17,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,18,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, as well as
OL,19,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates, 65, in
OL,20,Fthe early hours of June 13 last year.
