OL,7,FHe admitted manslaughter by diminished
OL,8,Fresponsibility and pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fthe attempted murder of three people
OL,10,Fwho were hit by a van stolen from Mr
OL,11,FCoates, after Nottingham Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard he had been diagnosed with
OL,13,Fparanoid schizophrenia.
