OL,7,FBut there was an outcry of anger from
OL,8,Fthe victims' families after
OL,9,Fprosecutors decided not to pursue
OL,10,Fmurder charges for Calocane, prompting
OL,11,FAttorney General Victoria Prentis to
OL,12,Forder a review of how the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service handled the case
OL,14,Fand ask the Court of Appeal to review
OL,15,Fthe sentence.
