OL,7,FInspector of Constabulary Roy Wilsher
OL,8,Fsaid: "We move police forces into our
OL,9,Fenhanced level of monitoring, known as
OL,10,Fengage, when a force is not responding
OL,11,Fto our concerns, or if it is not
OL,12,Fmanaging, mitigating or eradicating
OL,13,Fthese concerns.
OL,15,F"The engage process provides
OL,16,Fadditional scrutiny and support from
OL,17,Fthe inspectorate and other external
OL,18,Forganisations in the policing sector
OL,19,Fto help the force improve and provide
OL,20,Fa better service for the public.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
