OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner Caroline Henry said: "I
OL,9,Fam obviously disappointed that
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police is being placed
OL,11,Funder enhanced monitoring. However, I
OL,12,Fwelcome the opportunity this process
OL,13,Fwill provide the Force to focus on the
OL,14,Fareas of concern and continue their
OL,15,Fimmediate actions to put things right.
OL,17,F"As Police and Crime Commissioner, it
OL,18,Fis my duty to hold Nottinghamshire
OL,19,FPolice to account on behalf of the
OL,20,Fpublic and ensure we have the best
OL,21,Fpolicing service possible.
OL,26,@pD@cOUyD@AOU
