OL,7,F"The effective supervision of
OL,8,Finvestigations and ensuring the right
OL,9,Fsupport for victims are both vitally
OL,10,Fimportant to providing an effective
OL,11,Fpolicing service. Since HMICFRS raised
OL,12,Ftheir concerns with me, I have held
OL,13,Furgent discussions with the Chief
OL,14,FConstable and her team. I have sought
OL,15,Fassurances about the action being
OL,16,Ftaken and the plans the Chief
OL,17,FConstable has for improvements.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
