OL,7,F"I was assured to learn that the Force
OL,8,Fhad already taken immediate action.
OL,9,FThis should provide Nottinghamshire's
OL,10,Fcommunities with confidence that the
OL,11,FForce takes these concerns very
OL,12,Fseriously and is committed to making
OL,13,Fswift improvements.
