OL,7,F"I am determined to support and
OL,8,Foversee the Force's progress with
OL,9,Faddressing all HMICFRS'
OL,10,Frecommendations and have asked for
OL,11,Fweekly updates from the Chief
OL,12,FConstable. I am confident
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police will emerge a
OL,14,Fmuch stronger organisation as a result
OL,15,Fof the 'engage' process."
